metadata.name: Last trip
metadata.description:
Chapter 1. Last trip.

I have a special watch that others don't know. It allows me to travel back in time. The clock could turn back time up to a month. 

but I couldn't enjoy this ability. Because I'm destined to die. No matter what I do, I couldn't escape the fate of death. 

Numerous memories made with family and friends also disappeared after rewind a clock.

Today, Finally I decide to accept my fate. I threw the watch into the sea. Last trip is just begun.

Last trip(2022)
